author: Barnini Chakraborty
title: State Department leaked cables renew theories on origin of coronavirus
description: A Chinese laboratory at the center of new theories about how the coronavirus pandemic started was the subject of multiple urgent warnings inside the U.S. State Department two years ago, according to a new report.
